name: NYDailyNews
text:
Doug Emhoff, the husband of Kamala Harris, celebrated the first-ever ascension of a woman to the vice presidency.

Harris is becoming not only the first woman elected VP, but also the first Black person and the first Asian American voted into the position.
https://t.co/u76HFPhxWv

name: NYDailyNews
text:
Around 200 pro-Trump demonstrators, some of them openly carrying guns, gathered outside the Oregon state capital building in Salem to protest the election results.

The Trump supporters assaulted at least one cameraman and pepper-sprayed a woman.

https://t.co/rM1EG4BYlD
